{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was sort of my first invention amongst, later, others who just thought it has to be geared to survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we then-- we looked around if we find somebody who we knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in this particular camp, there was Jewish police like in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they then were transported to the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jewish police were dressed almost like the Polish police, and they had even ranks amongst them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ordinary, one stripe, two stripes, and even the highest one is three stripes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Hilowic, but he plays a role a bit later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father, amongst the police, found a cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, via this cousin, we got a little bit of food and a different job in the metal works.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think when we have a break now, I'm going to prepare a book to show you these things in the book.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because as we are speaking, we could have shown you that in a film where it was, because I have a sketch map of this particular camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, also at one time, I was introduced to a police with two stripes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His name was Salz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he gave me some food as well, being in, you know, in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He also would play another role later in my story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, it was a mighty change from working hard with little food to working not so hard in the metal works, metal workshop, with more food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Although it didn't come regular, but now and again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, the work in a metal workshop was that outside this, these barracks, was a very, very large heap of discarded metal of all sorts.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I only found out much after the war that it probably was from the famous Schindler's [?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
